citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 4:30pm on
07-Jun-17.
The inspector completed the inspection at site #001 and the facility representative for site #002 was not available for
the inspection.
